OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Fdry evening with late bright or sunny
OL,7,Fspells in the east and winds falling
OL,8,Flight. Dry overnight with clear spells
OL,9,Fin the east but remaining cloudy in
OL,10,Fwest.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FA dry morning with some bright
OL,13,Fspells in the east, but rain spreading
OL,14,Fto the west. The afternoon will be
OL,15,Fcloudy with outbreaks of rain, mainly
OL,16,Facross the west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
